# Walkthrough — Phase 2: Dynamic Product Engine + Comparison

## What Changed

Transformed DropGravity Pro from a static 8-product demo into a dynamic SaaS with:
- **Any keyword** generates realistic products (AI-simulated engine)
- **Versioned grading** tracks re-grade history
- **Side-by-side comparison** of up to 3 products
- **API-driven** everything — no more static mock filtering

